values:
they....made fun of me last night.
they didn't know, 
but- it hurt.

they laughed at my ribs...
my hip bones.



it made me feel even more self conscious...


I mean..it didn't help that I was already in a fucking bikini.




I hate myself.
D:
my heart hurts... and I can't breath... I feel like I've ran for hours on end- I just, can't catch my breath. It's only been one full day. suck it up.
